# Mapping

This section defines how external system data maps to the Payments Domain model.

## Payment Request Mapping

| External Field | Payment Domain Field |
| -------------- | -------------------- |
| orderId        | clientReferenceId    |
| totalAmount    | amount               |
| currencyCode   | currency             |
| customerId     | payerId              |
| merchantId     | payeeId              |

