## Status Mapping

| External Status | Internal Payment Status |
| --------------- | ----------------------- |
| CREATED         | Initiated               |
| PENDING         | Pending                 |
| SUCCESS         | Completed               |
| FAILED          | Failed                  |
| REFUNDED        | Refunded                |

